Title: Martial Eagle
Writer: Joseph Weisberg (creator), Tracey Scott Wilson (teleplay), Oliver North (story), Tracey Scott Wilson (story)
Actors: Keri Russell, Matthew Rhys, Annet Mahendru, Susan Misner
Plot: Philip and Elizabeth's long-planned mission turns ugly, impacting each of them in different ways. Stan digs in deeper at work as his personal life continues to unravel.
